@Node Edito "Editorial"

Heads up !
 
Welcome to  the  second edition  of Point  &  Rock. It's the number 2
and we have already  some changes  in the form. From now, the concert
dates  table will  offer you a  menu of  the bands. You won't have to
browse all the  table to  read the info  about the band that interest
you !

We  are also  a team  now. Please  welcome Ace... He will  supply you
articles about concert report  and album  tests. We have thought that
we could  create a Oldies but Goodies section where you can find some
old albums that you must listen to.

In this edition, you will find 2 concert  reports about @{"Metallica" Link MetInfo} and
@{"Soundgarden" Link SoundInfo} ( Paris and Brussels ). We give you  also a special bonus
with  the  lyrics  of @{"Load" Link Load}, the  latest  album  of the well known
Metallica. And also the charts.

Can I take  the  occasion to  recall you to vote for these charts. We
really need your opinion because a chart composed by the votes of two
guys, it's quite low !

So don't hesitate to read the @{"contribution" Link Contribution} section.

That's it for today, we  wish you a nice reading through the pages of
Point & Rock 2.



                                         Raphaël ^ Mister No/aßS

@Endnode

